'''Denil Daniel Castillo Preciado''' (born 24 March 2004) is an Ecuadorian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[FC Midtjylland]] and the [[Ecuador national football team|Ecuador national team]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sport.ua/uk/news/623701-ofitsiyno-shahtar-pidpisav-denilya-kastilyo|title=ОФІЦІЙНО. Шахтар підписав Деніля Кастільо}}</ref>

==Club career==
On 24 April 2023, [[FC Shakhtar Donetsk|Shakhtar Donetsk]] announced that they'd signed Castillo to a five-year contract from [[L.D.U. Quito|Liga de Quito]], commencing 1 July 2023.<ref>{{cite web |title=Denil Castillo is Shakhtar player |url=https://shakhtar.com/en/news/2023/april/24_news/24_denil-castillo/ |website=shakhtar.com |publisher=FC Shakhtar Donetsk |access-date=24 April 2023 |date=24 April 2023}}</ref>

Castillo signed a five-year deal with [[Danish Superliga]] side [[FC Midtjylland]] for a €4 million transfer fee on 1 July 2024.<ref>{{cite web |title=DENIL CASTILLO IS A NEW MAN AT FC MIDTJYLLAND |url=https://www.fcm.dk/nyheder/denil-castillo-er-ny-mand-i-fc-midtjylland/ |website=fcm.dk |publisher=FC Midtjylland |access-date=26 June 2024 |date=26 June 2024}}</ref> In March 2026 he extended his contract with Midtjylland until 2031.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sport.tv2.dk/live/fodbold/2024-12-19-brentford-henter-liverpool-keeper/fcm-forlaenger-med-midtbaneprofil?entry=b053d1a6-aaf9-412f-a294-d04a320cf6fd|publisher=TV2 Danmark|title=FCM forlænger med midtbaneprofil|date=10 March 2026|access-date=10 March 2026|language=da|trans-title=Midtjylland extends with midfielder}}</ref>

==International career==
Castillo has represented Ecuador at youth level.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://onefootball.com/en/news/si-lo-trabajan-bien-tenemos-companero-para-moises-por-mucho-tiempo-37189697|title=Si lo trabajan bien, tenemos compañero para Moisés por mucho tiempo|publisher=onefootball.com}}</ref>

==Style of play==
Castillo mainly operates as a central midfielder.<ref name="ec">{{Cite web|url=https://www.futbolecuador.com/site/noticia/antes-apuntabamos-a-brasil-ahora-cambiamos-la-orientacion-a-ecuador/154806|title="Antes apuntábamos a Brasil… Ahora cambiamos la orientación a Ecuador"|publisher=futbolecuador.com}}</ref>

